WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: zu

00:00:01.100 --> 00:00:07.020
 ukumboza izincwadi eziphezulu zesonto ezifana neLinux bias ngokusho kokhulumela 

00:00:07.020 --> 00:00:12.990
 oyisikhulu se-Twitter yenkampani uJack Dorsey utshele abasebenzi ngoLwesibili ukuthi abaningi babo 

00:00:12.990 --> 00:00:17.190
 bayovunyelwa ukusebenza ekhaya njalo nangokhalo 

00:00:17.190 --> 00:00:22.830
 ubhubhane lwegciwane luphela ku-imeyili eyaqala ukutholwa yizindaba ze-BuzzFeed uDorsey uthe 

00:00:22.830 --> 00:00:27.240
 bekulindelekile ukuthi i-Twitter ivule amahhovisi ayo ngaphambi kukaSepthemba nokuthi bonke abangenayo 

00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:30.210
 imicimbi yomuntu izokhanselwa kulo lonke unyaka 

00:00:30.210 --> 00:00:36.870
 inkampani izokwamukela ukuhlolwa kwezinhlelo zayo zemicimbi ka-2021 kungekudala kulo nyaka 

00:00:36.870 --> 00:00:41.190
 Isikhulumi sithe sikhethekile ukuthi siphendule ngokushesha futhi sivumele 

00:00:41.190 --> 00:00:44.899
 abantu ukuthi basebenze ekhaya kunikezwe ukugcizelela kwethu ukwabiwa kwezikhundla kanye 

00:00:44.899 --> 00:00:49.289
 ukusekela abasebenzi abasabalalisiwe abangasebenza kuphi 

00:00:49.289 --> 00:00:53.520
 ezinyangeni ezimbalwa ezedlule kufakazelwe ukuthi singawenza lowo msebenzi ukuze abasebenzi bethu babe 

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:57.840
 indima nesimo ezibenza bakwazi ukusebenza besuka ekhaya futhi bafuna ukuqhubeka 

00:00:57.840 --> 00:01:03.329
 ukwenza njalo kuze kube phakade sizokwenza ukuthi kwenzeke uma kungenjalo amahhovisi ethu azobe ekhona 

00:01:03.329 --> 00:01:07.619
 ukuzifudumeza nokwamukelekayo ngezindlela zokuphepha ezengeziwe lapho sizizwa zinjalo 

00:01:07.619 --> 00:01:12.119
 kuphephile ukubuyisa inqubomgomo entsha ye-Twitter njengoba kunamabhizinisi emhlabeni jikelele 

00:01:12.119 --> 00:01:16.500
 balwe nokuzivumelanisa nemihlahlandlela yokunciphiswa komphakathi futhi bacabange kabusha ukuthi bazokwenza kanjani 

00:01:16.500 --> 00:01:21.869
 zisebenza enkingeni yokuqothula izinkampani zomhlaba ezinkulu ze-tech ezifana ne-Facebook Google 

00:01:21.869 --> 00:01:26.250
 futhi iMicrosoft ibisheshe yathutha imodeli yokusebenzela ekhaya futhi nayo iye yaba 

00:01:26.250 --> 00:01:30.140
 oqapheleke kakhulu futhi uhlela ukuhambisa abasebenzi emuva ehhovisi 

00:01:30.140 --> 00:01:34.829
 U-Google utshele abasebenzi ukuthi iningi labo lizosebenza lisekhaya 

00:01:34.829 --> 00:01:40.590
 kuze kube ngu-2021 yize abanye bezobuya ekuqaleni kwehlobo i-Facebook ngokufanayo 

00:01:40.590 --> 00:01:44.680
 qala ukuvula kabusha amahhovisi ngemuva kwempelasonto kaJulayi 4 kodwa 

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:50.070
 abasebenzi abakwaziyo ukusebenza ukusuka ekhaya benza njalo kuze kube ngonyaka olandelayo 

